eventDataQuery: SELECT eventId, ANY_VALUE(title) as title, ANY_VALUE(description) as description, ANY_VALUE(emoji) as emoji, ANY_VALUE(startDate) as startDate, ANY_VALUE(endDate) as endDate, ANY_VALUE(marketingProgramInstanceId) as marketingProgramInstanceId, ANY_VALUE(eventType) as eventType, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT regionElement) as region, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT subRegionElement) as subRegion, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT countryElement) as country, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT activityOwnerElement) as activityOwner, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT speakersElement) as speakers, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT audiencePersonaElement) as audiencePersona, ARRAY_AGG(DISTINCT audienceSeniorityElement) as audienceSeniority, ANY_VALUE(eventSeries) as eventSeries, ANY_VALUE(emailLanguage) as emailLanguage, ANY_VALUE(emailText) as emailText, ANY_VALUE(languagesAndTemplates) as languagesAndTemplates, ANY_VALUE(accountSegments) as accountSegments, ANY_VALUE(customerUse) as customerUse, ANY_VALUE(okr) as okr, ANY_VALUE(gep) as gep, ANY_VALUE(activityType) as activityType, ANY_VALUE(accountSectors) as accountSectors, ANY_VALUE(maxEventCapacity) as maxEventCapacity, ANY_VALUE(peopleMeetingCriteria) as peopleMeetingCriteria, ANY_VALUE(landingPageLink) as landingPageLink, ANY_VALUE(salesKitLink) as salesKitLink, ANY_VALUE(hailoLink) as hailoLink, ANY_VALUE(publishedDate) as publishedDate, ANY_VALUE(lastEditedDate) as lastEditedDate FROM `google.com:cloudhub.data.master_event_data`, UNNEST(region) as regionElement, UNNEST(subRegion) as subRegionElement, UNNEST(country) as countryElement, UNNEST(activityOwner) as activityOwnerElement, UNNEST(speakers) as speakersElement, UNNEST(audiencePersona) as audiencePersonaElement, UNNEST(audienceSeniority) as audienceSeniorityElement GROUP BY eventId
